{"tid":1895485,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"斥美防疫過度 中國警告民眾：勿前往美國旅遊","createTime":"2020-02-24T14:29:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T14:42:28.000Z","uid":28114,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"92fc7211ae0b33bb2a83a18097b5d0332fa21d35","tid":1895485,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T14:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.rti.org.tw/assets/thumbnails/2019/04/05/20190405000089M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.rti.org.tw%2Fassets%2Fthumbnails%2F2019%2F04%2F05%2F20190405000089M.jpg&h=8e1c61f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國文化和旅遊部24日發出聲明，警告中國人民不要前往美國旅遊。(中央社資料照)<br />\n<br />\n中國文化和旅遊部今天(24日)發出聲明，警告中國人民不要前往美國旅遊，因為美國對俗稱武漢肺炎的「COVID-19」(2019年冠狀病毒疾病)疫情過度防範，使得中國觀光客在美國受到不公平待遇。<br />\n<br />\n聲明中說，「由於美國的過度防疫措施，以及美國國內的安全形勢，中國遊客在美國屢遭不公平對待，提醒中國遊客切實提高安全防範意識，切勿前往美國旅遊。」<br />\n<br />\n中國一再指責美國，認為美國對武漢肺炎疫情作出過度的反應，包括很早就限制來自中國的訪客等措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2052835?fbclid=IwAR3zE1ww2cMgXL4sbFb1oUF1eYZKxRkcV6QS4bP6NWHO9QFWn7Ax3nEMzBE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2052835%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3zE1ww2cMgXL4sbFb1oUF1eYZKxRkcV6QS4bP6NWHO9QFWn7Ax3nEMzBE&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwclSugA1I0CCabXjLbCjl00%3D&h=6791de26\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2052835?fbclid=IwAR3zE1ww2cMgXL4sbFb1oUF1eYZKxRkcV6QS4bP6NWHO9QFWn7Ax3nEMzBE</a>"},{"pid":"f301376aaafd7d3f0cce304aff8d5428a7351e66","tid":1895485,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T14:29:47.000Z","msg":"中共出大絕：乜都係歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef9ff7fc0ee7b1252c54a5351435743f66a7fc26","tid":1895485,"uid":190043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T14:32:32.000Z","msg":"大絕：自我封關<br />